{"type": "article", "id": 23100, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 24229, "name": "Göhlin"}, {"id": 24230, "name": "artori design"}, {"id": 24231, "name": "Jacqueline Bae"}, {"id": 24232, "name": "David Weeks"}, {"id": 24233, "name": "Santiago Landaburü"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110536179H5kp0ScTXeJ36.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Steel by Göhlin</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典家具公司 Göhlin 推出的 Steel 系列，有两款。椅腿和扶手几乎由一条极细的金属框架构成，流畅的曲线让椅子显得简洁轻盈，是极简金属风格。另一款在椅子在靠背、座位和扶手上采用了皮垫，但金属结构依然保留了下来，是向舒适性的改进。<a href=\"http://steelbygohlin.se\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154435RLmt2eXq93P7Qz0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154435rsULWh2TIC3aKBHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154436cQeRJniz0r5SIMXq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154436ZzS2TbHqiQ84oFn9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154437D4EbkVzygSnpJsqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47457627\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>UNDER THE SEA Light by David Trubridge </h2>\n<p>这组灯灵感源于海洋中的生物，比如硅藻、喙头舟形藻，使用 CNC 加工后的弯曲的竹材料，让它们有轻微的旋转感觉，很轻盈。光源在中间，能顺着镂空的结构投下漂亮的阴影。设计师长期生活在新西兰因而与海洋有密切的接触，<a href=\"http://www.davidtrubridge.com\">这里是设计师主页</a>，他的很多灯都用纤细的竹结构做这种镂空的立体效果。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154437ONIq6LkohZifRFzu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154437rPKN9u5SZJO2gYWp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544386UJgMmY0W4wjT7nb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154439N1f6gjR4am3hJ0cV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154439rJT2SI3Xc0QVnAyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>louis &amp; Ole by artori design</h2>\n<p>这是以色列工作室 artori 推出的挂钩系列，采用剪影的方式，勾画出黑猫和舞女两种图案。黑猫是专门挂在桌边的，有多种形态，比如将头、身体和手都越过了桌面而伸展到桌下，形成了挂钩。舞女则一手高扬挥动扇子，仿佛弗拉明戈舞者，下面悬挂的帕子可以让“她”变得摇曳多姿。这两款挂钩都非常生动，售价 14.9 美元，<a href=\"http://www.artoridesign.com\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154439LUJg4B8Nojr1QRiO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154440ue83st1MUw2dKhmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19315403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154440e1smZigvUraz8Dyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154441i3nlw78Y40OHaQ9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544416GgN29tDTrMncqVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.54645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>paper cones speaker by Jacqueline Bae</h2>\n<p>这是一个可改变大小的扬声器，它是圆锥形的。沿着中轴可以将它卷起来以放大或缩小扬声器，以此来调整音量的大小，是简单而有趣的设计，它回归了改变音量大小的原理。设计师出身于韩国，目前在美国就学，产品受到 nendo 的启发，目前还是一个概念。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544427HMC8KDxmf1P3LX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154442U2k3tbfvgTFOhiQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154443mjqk6CVKIrBgpt7U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154443L8p4zdki6ySmevNr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544445QcdI0OuBCv3oTN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>wooden Cubebot toy by David Weeks</h2>\n<p>这个立方体积木来自纽约设计师 David Weeks，灵感源于日本 Shinto Kumi-ki 积木。不同小块之间用弹性皮筋连接，可以拆解出一个立体的机器人，它的每一个关节都可以活动，非常灵活。设计师认为其简单的造型和木头本身的温润手感都是它受欢迎的原因。它由美国公司 Areaware 生产出多种颜色和型号，<a href=\"http://www.areaware.com/collections/all\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154444IjKpsR4h9Z0D786c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544448KNGmuFDhwlBQMTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154445m6iFrsZzch2un1vI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544450TSA95gCmpEauHwB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154446YqhHZbjw8UIoFuCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cacao Journey Club branding by Santiago Landaburü</h2>\n<p>The Cacao Journey Club 是中美洲厄瓜多尔的巧克力店和供应商，他们和当地设计师 Santiago Landaburü 都认为，巧克力是上天给当地的礼物，在设计 logo 时就用了可可豆的元素，是一个大的被剥开的可可豆。一种形式是在白底上描黑线，另一种在黑底上用金色的图案填充，可以见到清晰纹路和立体质感，很有辨识度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544467QHwOVjxnU3KMXSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63283582\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154446WnSvocasGhNOYxMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154447IvBpsNd89XuRygHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60096931\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154447MqFlvkaQpy5Hhb1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154448BpFladEongSHUX7c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061544482OP8txd5qGzIfBiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}